The paper deals with physical layer authentication in communication systems, which involves the use of machine learning techniques to improve the reliability and robustness of authentication. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Information Theory (cs.IT), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI). However, given the focus on physical layer authentication and the use of kernel machines and least-mean-square algorithms, cs.IT and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories.
